input.sql:
select 
      ACCOUNT_ID AS AccountId
      , TRX_DATE AS ActivityDate
      , null as ID
      , null as JournalTypeId
      , null as JournalSubTypeId
      , TRX_PARTNER_MDM_PARTY_ID AS MDM_Account_ID__c
      , MEMBER_ID AS MemberId
      , null as ProductId
      , null as Offering_ID__c
      , ACCOUNT_TYPE AS SFDC_Account_Type__c
      , CONCAT(SOURCE_ID,'-Estimates') AS Source_Id
      ,'Rebates - Estimate' AS Source_System__c
      , USAGE_TYPE AS UsageType
      ,'#{_dp('{"pill_type":"job_context","path":["user_name"]}')}' AS USER_NAME__C
      ,'Pending' AS Status
      ,'#{_dp('{"pill_type":"output","provider":"workato_variable","line":"3e8f2206","path":["uat_loyalty_record_id"]}')}'AS RecordTypeId
      , PARTNER_ALIGNMENT_FOR_REBATES AS Aligned_Distributor__c
      , TRX_NUMBER AS Associate_Opportunites__c
      , TRX_DATE_FISCAL_QUARTER_SHORTNAME AS ExternalTransactionNumber
      , null as Financial_Partner_ID__c
      , TRX_CRM_FORECAST_CATEGORY AS Forecast_Category__c
      , TRX_SPLIT_COVERAGE_SEGMENT AS Industry
      , PRODUCT_SPLIT_OFFERING_GROUP AS Product_Split_Offering_Group__c
      , ORDERED_QUANTITY_MIN AS Quantity
      , null as Renewal__c
      , ACV_AMOUNT_USD_CY_PR_WITH_HCS_DRAWDOWN AS TransactionAmount
      , TRX_COUNTRY_OF_ORDER AS TransactionLocation
      , TRANSACTION_TYPE as Transaction_Type__c
      , CURRENT_TIMESTAMP AS JOURNALDATE
 from PARTNERPROGRAMS_DB.MARTS.REBATES_STAGE_TJ
 where transaction_journal_id is null
 and UPPER(TRX_CRM_FORECAST_CATEGORY) = 'CLOSED'
 and TRX_DATE_FISCAL_QUARTER_SHORTNAME = 'Q' || QUARTER(CURRENT_DATE) || ' ' || RIGHT(YEAR(CURRENT_DATE), 2)
